data.description: GET THE MOST FOR YOUR $$$!!! Here's your chance to purchase a solid brick home on the water with inground pool at a price you can afford. Inviting front entry with white picket fence invites you in. Large den with fireplace & plenty of natural light. Kitchen has pretty Thomasville cabinets, stainless steel appliances (including refrigerator) & 2 pantries. Primary bedroom down with 2 additional spacious bedrooms up. Relaxing a/c cooled sunroom overlooks the inground pool, dock & boat hoist that holds up to 4500 pounds. Extras include...2016 HVAC heat pump with programmable thermostat, 2022 new windows with warranty, 2022 new roof, gutters, 2 attics, 2012 new hurricane shutters, no carpet, real white oak floors upstairs, oversized 20x26 garage, assumable flood insurance & brinks fire & security alarm system that stays.
